Package space.sunqian.fs.app.di

Interface InjectedResource

public interface InjectedResource
Represents resource of InjectedApp, consisting of a type and a singleton instance of that type. InjectedResources with the same raw class but different generic type parameters are considered distinct and are not equal to each other.
